{
  "texts": [
    "In the estimation process, developers can determine whether a service is worth developing based on user needs and use case examples to assess technical difficulty and costs.",
    "LLMs are particularly useful for automating development, allowing the generation of code by using service specifications and upcycling cases as input.",
    "The core outcome of this method is the realization of a process that automatically provides rich resources to comprehensively support service development.",
    "ImplementationI will provide a detailed explanation of the LLM used in the implementation.",
    "The interactive need extraction system from our prior research utilizes an LLM."
  ]
}